						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">sonder wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">what's bus masking though?<br /></div>What rainwarrior said. Specifically, one could pixelate the Y axis by having an AND or OR gate and three latched bits; something like CHRROM A[0..2] = AND(PPU A[0..2],LATCH0..2). <br />The X axis would be a much messier transformation; I don't see a way to do it short of a full multiplexer.</div>

