						<div class="postbody">Yes, building a mapper that would allow mosaic of sizes 2, 4 and 8 both horizontally and vertically would actually be quite simple !<br />It's a shame this wasn't added to MMC5 for instance.<br /><br />This can still easily be done in software (if CHR-RAM), though this will eat up CPU time and VRAM bandwith, or in hardware with CHR-ROM by wasting banks (Mega Man 5 does this). Not as cool as a mapper doing it !<br /><br />Mosaic of other sizes would be hell of a nightmare to realize, even on a mapper.</div>

